we  have  the  system  in  place.  All  we  need  is  the  commitment  to 
carry this out. And I think with your commitment, we can do this. 

So I look forward to working with you, Mr. Gutierrez——
Mr. GUTIERREZ. Thank you, Senator. 
Senator  INOUYE.—to  assure  that  our  Department  has  adequate 
resources to address this matter and fulfil your many other impor-
