And I’ll wait for my second turn. 
Mr. GUTIERREZ. Thank you, Senator. 
The  CHAIRMAN.  Well,  let  me  just  take  this  occasion,  Mr.  Sec-
retary,  if  you  will—I’d  like  to  introduce  the  Chief  of  Staff  of  the 
