viously without any authorization. And one of the great assets that 
we have as a country are our brands, our technology. 

So  I  agree,  I  think  this  is  a  matter  to  focus  on.  I  think  it  is  a 
big  issue,  and  I  know  it’s  a  matter  of  great  concern  to  you,  as  it 
