STATEMENT OF HON. TRENT LOTT,
U.S. SENATOR FROM MISSISSIPPI 

Senator LOTT. Well, thank you, Mr. Chairman. And I’m delighted 
to be here this afternoon, with you presiding for the first time over 
this  Committee.  I’m  looking  forward  to  an  exciting  2  years  under 
your leadership. 

I  want  to  say  how  proud  I  am  to  have  the  new  Members,  and 
I’ve  already  been  visiting,  on  both  sides  of  the  aisle,  and  I’ve  been 
